comments: Labissiere (POR) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm as he dislodges the ball at the end of the drive.
There is no conclusive angle showing whether Gobert (UTA) steps on the baseline while in possession of the ball.
Labissiere (POR) is firming up in a picking position in O'Neale's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Bogdanovic (UTA) briefly engages Simons (POR) off-ball before disengaging from the contact.
McCollum (POR) leans out of his driving trajectory as he initiates some contact with Ingles (UTA), but the contact is marginal during the drive.
Following the screen Simons (POR) briefly engages with Bogdanovic (UTA) and disengage off ball.
Labissiere (POR) briefly grasps Gobert's (UTA) jersey, but the contact to Gobert's uniform does not prevent him from getting to the rebound.
Labissiere (POR) sets the pick in O'Neale's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
During the pick, Ingles (UTA) briefly engages Labissiere (POR) before disengaging from the contact.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Anthony's (POR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) is not in a legal guarding position when he dislodges Lillard (POR) during the inbound prior to the ball being released.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Anthony (POR) extends his arm across O'Neale's (UTA) body and makes contact with his head during the inbound prior to the ball being released.
Simons (POR) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) absorbs contact from Lillard's (POR) body before cleanly blocking the driving shot attempt.
Simons (POR) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (UTA).
